<li><strong>Static analysis</strong>: Ignores technological change
reducing cost of living</li>
<li><strong>Narrow revenue view</strong>: Overlooks government
efficiency gains and restructuring</li>
<li><strong>Old economic models</strong>: Doesn’t account for
cryptocurrency-enabled value creation</li>
</ol>
