<ul>
<li>UBI provides safety net for risk-taking</li>
<li>More businesses started = more jobs created</li>
<li>Net employment effect may be positive</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Better job matching</strong>
<ul>
<li>People leave miserable jobs</li>
<li>Find work aligned with skills and interests</li>
<li>Productivity increases (happy workers are productive workers)</li>
</ul></li>
