<h2 id="beyond-survival-thriving">Beyond Survival: Thriving</h2>
<p>This isn’t about returning to subsistence farming or becoming
off-grid survivalists. It’s about <strong>technology-enabled
abundance</strong> where individuals have genuine choice:</p>
